    </div>
    <div class="qbody">
      <div class="ans">
        <div class="def"><strong>Definition:</strong> An Operating System is a software program that manages a computer's hardware and software resources, providing a platform for applications to run. It acts as an intermediary between hardware and the user.</div>
        <div class="dw">
