        <h4>Duties Performed</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Process Management:</strong> Creates, schedules, and terminates processes; handles synchronisation and communication between processes.</li>
          <li><strong>Memory Management:</strong> Allocates and deallocates memory; implements virtual memory and memory protection.</li>
          <li><strong>I/O Management:</strong> Controls I/O devices through device drivers; manages buffering and data transfer.</li>
          <li><strong>File System Management:</strong> Organises files and directories; manages file access, permissions, and storage allocation.</li>
