      <h3>Describe differences among short-term, medium-term, and long-term scheduling. Does swapping improve or degrade system efficiency? Can it be used in multiprogramming? <span class="ytag">2022</span></h3>
      <span class="qtog">▼</span>
    </div>
    <div class="qbody">
      <div class="ans">
        <table class="tbl">
          <tr><th>Feature</th><th>Short-Term</th><th>Medium-Term</th><th>Long-Term</th></tr>
          <tr><td>Also called</td><td>CPU scheduler</td><td>Swapper</td><td>Job scheduler</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Purpose</td><td>Pick next process for CPU</td><td>Swap processes in/out of memory</td><td>Admit jobs to memory from job queue</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Frequency</td><td>Very frequent (ms)</td><td>Occasional (seconds–minutes)</td><td>Infrequent (minutes–hours)</td></tr>
