      <h3>Disk queue: 98,183,37,122,14,134,65,67 (head at 53). Calculate total head movements using SSTF. Mention disadvantages. <span class="ytag">2024</span></h3>
      <span class="qtog">▼</span>
    </div>
    <div class="qbody">
      <div class="ans">
        <p>SSTF (Shortest Seek Time First) services the request with the minimum seek distance from the current head position at each step.</p>
        <table class="tbl">
          <tr><th>Step</th><th>Head</th><th>Chosen</th><th>Distance</th></tr>
          <tr><td>1</td><td>53</td><td>65</td><td>12</td></tr>
          <tr><td>2</td><td>65</td><td>67</td><td>2</td></tr>
          <tr><td>3</td><td>67</td><td>37</td><td>30</td></tr>
          <tr><td>4</td><td>37</td><td>14</td><td>23</td></tr>
          <tr><td>5</td><td>14</td><td>98</td><td>84</td></tr>
          <tr><td>6</td><td>98</td><td>122</td><td>24</td></tr>
          <tr><td>7</td><td>122</td><td>134</td><td>12</td></tr>
          <tr><td>8</td><td>134</td><td>183</td><td>49</td></tr>
        </table>
        <div class="note"><strong>Total Head Movements = 12+2+30+23+84+24+12+49 = 236 cylinders</strong></div>
        <h4>Disadvantages of SSTF</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Starvation:</strong> Requests at far cylinders may wait indefinitely if new requests keep arriving near the current head position.</li>
